    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i'm being forced to endure something that shouldn't be endured. like, why is the expectation always to just \"push through\" when the thing that makes life worth it is gone? it feels more like a punishment than living. do you really think people are supposed to just suffer through this kind of emptiness forever?",
